#: ../../source/network/http/cookie.rst:2
msgid "Cookie"
msgstr "Cookie"

#: ../../source/network/http/cookie.rst:5
msgid "简介"
msgstr "Introduction"

#: ../../source/network/http/cookie.rst:6
msgid "Cookie（复数形态Cookies），类型为「小型文本文件」，指某些网站为了辨别用户身份而储存在用户本地终端上的数据。"
msgstr "Cookies are small text files stored on a user's local device by some websites to identify the user."

#: ../../source/network/http/cookie.rst:9
msgid "属性"
msgstr "Attributes"

#: ../../source/network/http/cookie.rst:12
msgid "name"
msgstr "name"

#: ../../source/network/http/cookie.rst:13
msgid "cookie的名称。"
msgstr "The name of the cookie."

#: ../../source/network/http/cookie.rst:16
msgid "value"
msgstr "value"

#: ../../source/network/http/cookie.rst:17
msgid "cookie的值。"
msgstr "The value of the cookie."

#: ../../source/network/http/cookie.rst:20
msgid "expires"
msgstr "expires"

#: ../../source/network/http/cookie.rst:21
msgid "当 Expires 属性缺省时，表示是会话性 Cookie，在用户关闭浏览器时失效。"
msgstr "When the Expires attribute is omitted, the cookie is a session cookie and becomes invalid when the user closes the browser."

#: ../../source/network/http/cookie.rst:24
msgid "max-age"
msgstr "max-age"

#: ../../source/network/http/cookie.rst:25
msgid ""
"max-age 可以为正数、负数、0。如果 max-age 属性为正数时，浏览器会将其持久化，当 max-age 属性为负数，则表示该 "
"Cookie 只是一个会话性 Cookie。当 max-age 为 0 时，则会立即删除这个 Cookie。Expires 和 max-age "
"都存在的条件下，max-age 优先级更高。"
msgstr ""
"max-age can be a positive number, a negative number, or 0. If the "
"max-age attribute is positive, the browser persists the cookie. If "
"max-age is negative, the cookie is only a session cookie. When max-age "
"is 0, the cookie is deleted immediately. If both Expires and max-age are "
"present, max-age takes precedence."

#: ../../source/network/http/cookie.rst:28
msgid "domain"
msgstr "domain"

#: ../../source/network/http/cookie.rst:29
msgid "指定Cookie的域名，默认是当前域名。domain设置时可以设置为自身及其父域，子域可以访问父域的Cookie，反之不能。"
msgstr "Specifies the cookie's domain name. The default is the current domain. When domain is set, it can be set to the current domain or a parent domain. Subdomains can access cookies for a parent domain, but not the other way around."

#: ../../source/network/http/cookie.rst:32
msgid "path"
msgstr "path"

#: ../../source/network/http/cookie.rst:33
msgid "指定一个 URL 路径，这个路径必须出现在要请求的资源的路径中才可以发送对应的 Cookie。"
msgstr "Specifies a URL path. This path must appear in the path of the requested resource for the corresponding cookie to be sent."

#: ../../source/network/http/cookie.rst:36
msgid "secure"
msgstr "secure"

#: ../../source/network/http/cookie.rst:37
msgid "只能通过 HTTPS 传输。"
msgstr "Can only be transmitted over HTTPS."

#: ../../source/network/http/cookie.rst:40
msgid "httponly"
msgstr "httponly"

#: ../../source/network/http/cookie.rst:41
msgid "限制Cookie仅在HTTP传输过程中被读取，一定程度上防御XSS攻击。"
msgstr "Restricts the cookie to being read only during HTTP transmission, which helps defend against XSS attacks to some extent."

#: ../../source/network/http/cookie.rst:44
msgid "SameSite"
msgstr "SameSite"

#: ../../source/network/http/cookie.rst:45
msgid ""
"SameSite 支持 Strict / Lax / None 三种值。Strict最为严格，完全禁止第三方 "
"Cookie，跨站点时，任何情况下都不会发送 Cookie。Lax 允许部分第三方请求携带 Cookie，主要是链接、预加载、GET "
"表单三种情况。Cookie 的 SameSite 属性为 None ，且设置了 Secure 时，无论是否跨站都会发送 Cookie。"
msgstr ""
"SameSite supports three values: Strict, Lax, and None. Strict is the "
"most restrictive value and completely blocks third-party cookies; cookies "
"are never sent in cross-site situations. Lax allows some third-party "
"requests to carry cookies, mainly links, preloading, and GET forms. When "
"a cookie's SameSite attribute is None and Secure is set, the cookie is "
"sent regardless of whether the request is cross-site."
